From mlee Malcolm Lee Subject Re A KIND and LOVING God In article writes In article mlee Malcolm Lee writes BTW David Koresh was NOT Jesus Christ as he How can you tell for sure Three days haven't passed Well where is he Another false Messiah shot down in Matthew Watch out that no one deceives For many will come in my name claiming 'I am the Christ' and will deceive Matthew At that time if anyone says to you 'Look here is the Christ ' or 'There he is ' do not believe For false Christs and false prophets will appear and perform great signs and miracles to deceive even the elect if that were See I have told you ahead of Do we listen Sadly not all of us Peace be with you and condolences to the families of those lost at Malcolm Lee Steve Bittrolff The previous is my opinion and is shared by any reasonably intelligent